{"tid":251972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英：要透過民事及刑事遏止梁繼昌手段","createTime":"2017-05-21T11:23:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-21T17:10:59.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6f53ddef7f3c7e718f569c8a824d3ae411707a14","tid":251972,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T11:23:07.000Z","msg":"行政長官梁振英4日內第3度就UGL事件發表網誌。他向立法會會計界議員梁繼昌發公開信，引述對方社交網站舊帖文，包括要求稅務局局長調查他，質疑這些「利用執法機關打擊政府官員的手段，必須用民事及刑事手段遏止」。<br />\n<br />\n委員會委員、民主黨林卓廷認為，梁振英多次要求梁繼昌辭去委員會職務，是干預委員會工作。"},{"pid":"3ffdd0b7dd5a92946643f37b77e039412eea2ac9","tid":251972,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T11:23:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1331568-20170521.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1331568-20170521.htm&d=zEdRUiHPsyXb%2F8eFbI6WSE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=b52c5999\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1331568-20170521.htm&h=94394e96\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1331568-20170521.htm</a>"},{"pid":"52f4cc3cc0dd466306b796bca986008cc0efe196","tid":251972,"uid":45821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T11:24:52.000Z","msg":"689要呷尿片未？"},{"pid":"903852151344fb80515b9e1e722f956275d881d7","tid":251972,"uid":40851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T11:25:51.000Z","msg":"擺明身有屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d13a371c0f57fcbaad5f5601e9c9a4d57120a6e","tid":251972,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T11:26:28.000Z","msg":"「<span style=\"color: red;\">利用執法機關打擊政府官員的手段，必須用民事及刑事手段遏止」</span><br />\n犯左邊條罪,係咪不誠實使用電腦"},{"pid":"df35ffe5966ecf80f3a1b9f35fd836f895e49928","tid":251972,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T13:08:18.000Z","m